        "timestamp": "2019-11-20 21:26:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI think Pam mentioned that master has some issues.. \nAlthough, I just remembered that Sonar jobs track only master :(\nUnless we are planning for tech teams repos master branch to point to this future release from elalto oparent",
